**Describe the bug**

X bot doesn't reply to any mentions at all. Polling works, Posting works, but bot ignores all mentions.

**To Reproduce**

- Install elizaOS
- add twitter logins and LLM API on .env (also using plugin-dkg but that does not trigger when my bot does not manage to reply to mentions)
- run a character

**Expected behavior**

Replying to TWITTER_TARGET_USERS when mentioned. However, I see INSTRUCTIONS on the logs but nothing happens and LLM does not make a decision, and then INSTRUCTIONS keep on looping. Logs also say already responded to tweet but bot did not answer anything. Polling seems to work, actions like retweeting and liking are fine, but responding to mentions do not work. 

